From: Anson Huang <Anson.Huang@nxp.com>
Date: Thu, 10 May 2018 14:17:48 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 3765/5242] MLK-18265-3 ARM64: dts: freescale: imx8qm: correct
 usb power domain

commit  abb42286e64ddb3c96285e2a17cde19f9842447d from
https://source.codeaurora.org/external/imx/linux-imx.git

Correct USB power domain tree to make sure kernel can
boot up successfully with XRDC enforcement enabled.

Signed-off-by: Anson Huang <Anson.Huang@nxp.com>
Reviewed-by: Bai Ping <ping.bai@nxp.com>
Tested-by: Peng Fan <peng.fan@nxp.com>
Signed-off-by: Meng Li <Meng.Li@windriver.com>
---
 .../boot/dts/freescale/fsl-imx8qm-device.dtsi      |   15 +++++++++------
 1 file changed, 9 insertions(+), 6 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-imx8qm-device.dtsi b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-imx8qm-device.dtsi
index 4d379c3..b5a1882 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-imx8qm-device.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-imx8qm-device.dtsi
@@ -350,14 +350,17 @@
 			pd_conn_usb2: PD_CONN_USB_2 {
 				reg = <SC_R_USB_2>;
 				#power-domain-cells = <0>;
+				#address-cells = <1>;
+				#size-cells = <0>;
 				power-domains = <&pd_conn>;
 				wakeup-irq = <271>;
-			};
-			pd_conn_usb2_phy: PD_CONN_USB_2_PHY {
-				reg = <SC_R_USB_2_PHY>;
-				#power-domain-cells = <0>;
-				power-domains = <&pd_conn>;
-				wakeup-irq = <271>;
+
+				pd_conn_usb2_phy: PD_CONN_USB_2_PHY {
+					reg = <SC_R_USB_2_PHY>;
+					#power-domain-cells = <0>;
+					power-domains = <&pd_conn_usb2>;
+					wakeup-irq = <271>;
+				};
 			};
 			pd_conn_sdch0: PD_CONN_SDHC_0 {
 				reg = <SC_R_SDHC_0>;
